  "remarks": "\nJoint Stock Company (JSC) Genbank is a Russian financial institution that operates extensively in the occupied territory of Crimea. By providing banking and other financial services in the annexed territory of Crimea it contributes to undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine.\n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
